4- Create dtb for VM spawning
5- Create stage 2 page tables per guest
7- Define guest context save/restore structures
8- Implement HVC trap handler
9- Implement full guest context save/restore
10- Implement switching logic within hypervisor
11- Implement blocking HVCs: send/wait and receive/wait
12- Write minimal guest kernels (20 lines each)
13- Create guest HVC wrapper assembly stubs


